Software AG Moves IDS Holding Into New Subsidiary, FTD Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-03-28T06:35:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/software-ag-moves-ids-holding-into-new-subsidiary-ftd-reports.html
Software AG (SOW)  is putting parts of its
IDS Scheer stake into a new subsidiary, partly to save on tax,
the  Financial Times Deutschland  reported today, without saying
where it got the information.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
